$ ================================================================
$ RBE3 INTERPOLATION
$ Accelerometers: G6 (X=5), G8 (X=7), G11 (X=10)
$ Fixed root:     G1 (X=0), G101 (X=0,Y+1), G1002 (X=0,Y-1)
$ DOF 3 = Z translation (vertical bending)
$
$ Linear interpolation weights: wt proportional to distance from
$ each anchor.  expand_rbe3_displacements seeds any independent
$ GRID absent from meas_disps at zero, so the root BC is honoured.
$
$ ---- Main spine (Y=0) ------------------------------------------
$ Segment root(X=0) -> G6(X=5)
RBE3, 200, ,  2, 3, 4.0, 3,  1,  1.0, 3,  6
RBE3, 201, ,  3, 3, 3.0, 3,  1,  2.0, 3,  6
RBE3, 202, ,  4, 3, 2.0, 3,  1,  3.0, 3,  6
RBE3, 203, ,  5, 3, 1.0, 3,  1,  4.0, 3,  6
$ Segment G6(X=5) -> G8(X=7)
RBE3, 210, ,  7, 3, 1.0, 3,  6,  1.0, 3,  8
